
##
## serverM README
##

serverM V2.2 (*nix)
By David Scholefield port80.com (serverm@port80.com)
serverM website http://www.serverm.org

see serverM user manual distributed with system
(docs/manual.pdf)

REQUIREMENTS

		Perl 5+
		Perl libraries:
		Cwd
		Digest::MD5
		File::Find
		File::Basename
		POSIX
		Net::SMTP
		MIME::Lite
		Storable
		Sys::Syslog
		Crypt::CBC
		Crypt::Blowfish

        
INSTALLATION

        ./configure
        ./serverM -D

KNOWN ISSUES

        None currently, but please report any that you find

